{"tid":2388011,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係唔慣用msg而係鐘意面對面傾偈","createTime":"2021-01-30T18:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T10:17:34.000Z","uid":249586,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d9881205a69b109fcb5e79087799c66ad9b2bab1","tid":2388011,"uid":249586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:30:13.000Z","msg":"發覺自己真係唔多識用訊息r水吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都好似尷尷尬尬咁<br />\n無論係朋友同同事都係咁<br />\n搞到好似同人好疏遠<br />\n成日望到人哋好多個msg好close咁就好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果係面對面傾偈就好smooth <br />\n亦都鐘意約出嚟傾多啲<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都有同樣嘅情況？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d1ed752784883fb653287a130ba66471386144","tid":2388011,"uid":369643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:32:08.000Z","msg":"無計啦"},{"pid":"3bb41839c9ca5b89c201d02198ab79baa4151735","tid":2388011,"uid":72418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T19:01:48.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔鐘意打字打到長一長，平時一句起兩句止。<br />\n有時覆覆下唔想再伸延話題，覺得好夾硬黎，就已讀不回，都係鐘意有咩就約出黎見面講"},{"pid":"997258c66a9699c0a687bf37eaa994d8904fe058","tid":2388011,"uid":139437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:14:26.000Z","msg":"我面對面係好撚多嘢講<br />\n但係一用msg就好似唔識講嘢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話題嗰啲完全唔識接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲msg唔係講正經嘢就係約人出嚟吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3063cd413b9990f1934d05fffdb844668ee6b4a","tid":2388011,"uid":369015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />調轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj